originalText.text: The way in which they handle insurance payments for the visits and treatments is extremely sketchy. Here is my experience with MTH. They came to our office and provided us a free 30 mins therapy. I had little back issue and went to Manhattan Total Health to visit doctor and know what's wrong. I met with a doctor and she tried to explain me what might be wrong. After that doctor started asking me to have a massage therapy immediately but I didn't show any interest. Then she suggested to have PT or Acupuncture. I was taken to another room where then did ultra sound, which I didn't expect. And that too only one side.  And they told me that they will do the other side in next visit. And finally I had PT.  Receptionist suggested that I need to have PT at least 2 times a week and tried to book for another day. I said NO and came out. And they claimed 1100$ from my insurance.     STAY AWAY from this Place.
